To download ntc_tempate
**********************

sudo apt update
sudo apt install git //if you don't have git
git clone https://github.com/networktocode/ntc-templates.git

To install Genie Parser
**********************
sudo apt update
sudo pip3 install genie
sudo pip3 install pyats

To install NAPALM getters
*************************
sudo apt update
sudo pip3 install nornir_napalm
